11/d/2">Pub. L. 115–232, div. A, title VI, § 611(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2018-08-13">Aug. 13, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/1797">132 Stat. 1797</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/116/92/dA/tVI/s611/d/2">Pub. L. 116–92, div. A, title VI, § 611(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2019-12-20">Dec. 20, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/1426">133 Stat. 1426</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/116/283/dA/tVI/s611/d/2">Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title VI, § 611(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/134/3673">134 Stat. 3673</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/81/dA/tVI/s611/d/2">Pub. L. 117–81, div. A, title VI, § 611(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2021-12-27">Dec. 27, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/1769">135 Stat. 1769</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/117/263/dA/tVI/s601/d/2">Pub. L. 117–263, div. A, title VI, § 601(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2022-12-23">Dec. 23, 2022</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/136/2619">136 Stat. 2619</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/118/31/dA/tVI/s613/d/2">Pub. L. 118–31, div. A, title VI, § 613(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2023-12-22">Dec. 22, 2023</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/137/291">137 Stat. 291</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/118/159/dA/tVI/s611/d/2">Pub. L. 118–159, div. A, title VI, § 611(d)(2)</ref>, <date date="2024-12-23">Dec. 23, 2024</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/138/1932">138 Stat. 1932</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/119/60/dA/tVI">Pub. L. 119–60, div. A, title VI</ref>, §§ 601(c)(2), 611(d)(2), <date date="2025-12-18">Dec. 18, 2025</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/139/902">139 Stat. 902</ref>, 906.)</sourceCredit>
